Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜很喜欢这个旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己编的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没画完呢 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊 过来拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克老师吗 他还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就像熊先生一样 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软啪啪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肥嘟嘟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来比起守卫 他更适合当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 谁来救救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧 雷欧 雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跳下来 我会接住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拿出勇气来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力哦 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你了 雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里也许还有其他人需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜不想见小义和小纱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没回来就去八丁镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那里后向官府求助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是久违的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什么值得兴奋的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与火之国接壤的边境小国的小村庄发生了惨案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说那里的居民惨遭灭门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亘古以来 那里就被视为圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称巨坑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传言那里藏有秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打击觊觎秘宝的盗贼们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里防守严密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军覆没也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽想尽可能增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但村里如今也不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前日发生的村外临时墓地被破坏事件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且封印着晓成员的森林里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那起镰刀被盗事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我们要忙上一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能无视平民们的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖出袭击村子的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予其应得的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都烧成灰烬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是用什么武器袭击村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壮观的树林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面明明是寸草不生的荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该是宝库吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的泉水应该通往某处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下竟有如此的空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被盗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想趁火打劫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是受命而来的木叶忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来调查这座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是守护附近八丁镇的警卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和托尼卡村交好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人向你引见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些贵客是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们如此迅速前来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫迪索纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是八丁镇的镇长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前日那些幸免于难的村民们前来求助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得知了此事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何入侵者的线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的守卫和觊觎秘宝的盗贼们有过多次冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道那个宝物到底是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕村里了解真相的也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说根本不知道是谁为了什么而袭击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的水真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这巨坑简直就像在吸收周围的活力和生息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讴歌着繁荣一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的泉水充满着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么爱打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这附近想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在做一些研究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些蛇是我用大蛇丸大人的细胞制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏其强大的再生力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹指间便能大量繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 借助我伟大的实验成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以移植其他生物的细胞核
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重现遗传信息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧合的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的水能够迅速促进细胞分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和病毒不相上下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是晓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 飞段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你出现在这里不是偶然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击村子的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好给我解释解释 说说经过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓得到…我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不会让你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋子并非就此一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是…晓的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师和疾风老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你盗的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道忍术的火候还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 千万别被对方碰到血液
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 快无法呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上古之神创造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被污秽之人夺去了力量
